							Digital Media
						</a>
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
						Interactive media and digital arts programs.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-2">
						<a href="/postgraduate/subject-guide/marketing" class="hover:text-blue-800">
							Marketing
						</a>
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
						Brand management and creative marketing strategies.
